93
00:04:18,625 --> 00:04:21,361 position:50%
by splitting the traffic
going to each page


94
00:04:21,361 --> 00:04:23,997 line:0
and measuring download
conversion on each,


95
00:04:23,997 --> 00:04:27,534 position:50%
you may learn that the treatment
page actually performs better,


96
00:04:27,534 --> 00:04:30,570 line:0
suggesting you may want to apply
the treatment metadata


97
00:04:30,570 --> 00:04:35,509 line:0
to your default product page
to improve overall conversion.


98
00:04:35,509 --> 00:04:36,843 position:50%
For your treatment page,


99
00:04:36,843 --> 00:04:40,313 line:0
