107
00:05:02,068 --> 00:05:04,104 line:0
of the total traffic.


108
00:05:04,104 --> 00:05:06,907 line:-1
When running a test
that involves the app icon,


109
00:05:06.907 --> 00:05:10.110 line:-1 position:50%
we've made sure that all users
who download your app


110
00:05:10,110 --> 00:05:12,078 line:-1
will have
a consistent experience.


111
00:05:12.078 --> 00:05:14.781 line:-1 position:50%
