is an important way


112
00:05:14,781 --> 00:05:16,650 line:-1
to appeal to App Store users


113
00:05:16,650 --> 00:05:18,752 line:-1
and stand out
on their home screens.


114
00:05:18,752 --> 00:05:21,121 line:-1
